{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_Sor2DthInit}}
'''A_Sor2DthInit'''<br />
(no parameters)

Kills all the monsters alive, friendly or not, and sets the calling actor's <tt>special1</tt> field to 7. This is used to make D'Sparil's death animation loop several times.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|Sorcerer2}} and derived classes.

[[Category:Decorate Heretic functions]] [[Category:Decorate Status change functions]] [[Category:Decorate Restricted functions]]{{DEFAULTSORT:Sor2DthInit}}
